      • getStripeSize

        public int getStripeSize()
        Description copied from interface: DifferentialStyleProvider
        This is the number of rows or columns in a band or stripe. For styles that represent stripes, it must be > 1, for all others it is 0. Not the greatest overloading by the OOXML spec.(这是带状或条纹中的行或列数。对于代表条纹的样式，它必须> 1，对于所有其他样式，它必须> 0。这并不是OOML规范中最大的超载。)
        Specified by:
        getStripeSize in interface DifferentialStyleProvider(界面中的getStripeSize DifferentialStyleProvider)
        Returns:
        number of rows/columns in a stripe for stripe styles, 0 for all others(条纹样式为条纹中的行/列数，所有其他样式为0)
